I mean, if you're running for office in that thing and it was based off of this stuff, you'd want this guy to run for office because you couldn't find anything wrong with me.

19:16.821 --> 19:17.522
He's done everything.

19:19.586 --> 19:26.855
And then they say, as far as in relation to Israel's enemies or in keeping with the law, not only did he follow the law, he had zeal.

19:27.255 --> 19:28.076
He had passion.

19:28.877 --> 19:31.240
And it seemed because he says, I persecuted the church.

19:32.442 --> 19:34.504
And people came against the law, came against what we're doing.

19:34.544 --> 19:36.667
It seemed like it was hitting against these Pharisees.

19:36.767 --> 19:39.550
Oh, I was one of the guys out there persecuting them.

19:39.570 --> 19:41.753
I was rounding up the men and women of the church.

19:41.853 --> 19:43.595
