26:54.527 --> 27:00.696
So it's not that he hates that, but it's when what he doesn't like here is when these guys are coming in and they're saying, no, no, that comes first.

27:01.017 --> 27:02.499
That's more important than Christ.

27:02.739 --> 27:15.577
And see, that's for me when I look at this, man, that's really the lesson to remember for me is what in my life do I have too high up on the profit statement as a gain that I should move over into the loss?

27:15.597 --> 27:21.586
In other words, what am I holding on too tightly that if Christ were to speak to me, he wanted to use me that

27:22.242 --> 27:26.168
I wouldn't see it, or I wouldn't say yes, because I care too much about this.

27:28.252 --> 27:29.894
Because I would say, well, what's it gonna cost me?

27:31.857 --> 27:36.104
And it's tough because every single one of you that are here, God has a purpose for you.

27:36.124 --> 27:36.846
