27:36.866 --> 27:40.451
He wants to use you in some way to share his love to the world.

27:42.575 --> 27:45.439
Sometimes we don't see it and we don't wanna be used because I don't want to.

27:45.459 --> 27:47.362
I might have to talk to someone.

27:47.382 --> 27:49.586
I might have to be nice and I don't like being nice.

27:50.850 --> 27:52.292
because these people drive me crazy.

27:52.994 --> 27:55.658
