28:14.629 --> 28:15.210
Oh, careful.

28:16.853 --> 28:17.714
Make sure that you're not,

28:17.858 --> 28:19.540
putting stuff that you do, because I'm sure you're good.

28:19.560 --> 28:20.881
I'm sure you're all here, wonderful people.

28:22.703 --> 28:25.847
